  <notes>
    The actual `AuditEnrichmentMiddleware` lives at `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Infrastructure/Logging/AuditEnrichmentMiddleware.cs` â€” task 043 extends it. This task does NOT touch the middleware; the middleware already enriches every authenticated request and Action endpoints inherit that enrichment automatically.

    `IActionOrchestrationService` is task 041's deliverable. This task depends on the *interface* shape via `IActionEngineFacade` (task 015). If you find yourself wanting to inject `IActionOrchestrationService` directly into an endpoint, STOP â€” that's the G12 violation. Go through the facade.

